recipesJson.name: Peachy Honeysuckle Cream
recipesJson.author: naiviv334
recipesJson.description: I made a batch with everything here minus Honeysuckle, (INW) Peach, and the two drops of (TPA) Honey. It was pretty good on it's own, but it was delicious when I used it to top off my tank that was halfway full of a honeysuckle flavored eliquid. Results TBA.
